<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Your Refund Request Has Been Approved</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
</head>

<body
    style="margin: 0; padding: 0; min-width: 100%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; background-color: #FAFAFA; color: #222222;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <div style="background-color: #4CAF50; padding: 24px; color: #ffffff;">
            <h1
                style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.25; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: center;">
                Refund Request Approved</h1>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 24px; background-color: #ffffff;">
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">Hello {{userName}},</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">Good news! Your refund request for order <strong>{{orderId}}</strong> has been approved.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">Refund Request ID: <strong>{{refundId}}</strong></p>
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">Reason provided: {{reason}}</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">The refund will be processed shortly.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact
                us.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 24px; text-align: center; color: #999999; font-size: 14px;">
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">&copy; {{year}} Your Store Name. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html> 